data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath house on an almost half-acre lot fulfills all your needs in the most convenient location! The bedrooms feature no carpet, and you'll adore the expansive entertainment room with a bar area, perfect for watching the game. A detached 2-car garage provides ideal storage or parking space. The large fenced-in backyard includes a spacious deck for all your entertainment needs. The roof was replaced in 2021, the HVAC system was upgraded in 2019, and the best part is that this neighborhood does not have an HOA!   * Buyer or buyer's agent to verify all pertinent information. *
